queries.sql: SELECT `books`.`book_id`, `books`.`title`, `books`.`description`, `books`.`isbn`, `books`.`img`, `books`.`pages`, `books`.`publish_date`, `books`.`amount`, GROUP_CONCAT(authors.name, ' ', authors.surname ORDER BY authors.name SEPARATOR ', ') as authors FROM `books` LEFT JOIN `book_author` ON `books`.`book_id` = `book_author`.`book_id` LEFT JOIN `authors` ON `authors`.`author_id` = `book_author`.`author_id` GROUP BY `books`.`book_id`, `books`.`title` LIMIT 10
